> Hey everyone.
>
> Regarding MLMA, due to shared control group, I wonder if:
>
> 1) Is it enough to code "studies/obs" and we are done?
>
> res_mlma <- rma.mv(yi, vi, random = ~ 1 | studies/obs, data=dat)
>
